<dl id="n12135a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12135a">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12135a"> 135(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> preacher comes / remove dung <small>Green</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="n12135a"><li>FW 447.14ff </li><li><a href="../../flex/qA/lexqA.htm#n12135a">2010</a> </li><li><a href="../../flex/qA/l39qA.htm#n12135a">1939</a> </li><li><ms href="#n12135a">MS BL 47483-117</ms> </li><li>JJA 57:184 <a name="qAd5" href="../../ff/fdra/qda.htm#qAd5">Usage</a> </li><li> <a href="../../flex/qA/qAd5.htm#n12135a">Draft: III&sect;2A.5</a></li> </ul> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[Imagining a small town on the eve of a visit of Vincent Ferrier]</font> Voil&agrave; trois jours que l&apos;on cloue des planches sur la grand&apos;place. On dresse &laquo;l&apos;&eacute;chafaud &raquo; du haut duquel le ma&icirc;tre s&apos;adressera au peuple. Des braves gens du pays sont venus donner un coup de main aux charpentiers. Il n&apos;est pas question d&apos;un salaire, mais ils savent bien qu&apos;ils toucheront un pourboire, et ils sont tellement persuad&eacute;s que le bon Dieu du ciel leur revaudra leur peine, qu&apos;ils ne pensent pas du tout avoir fait un m&eacute;tier de dupe. Un peu partout on enl&egrave;ve des tas de fumiers, peut-&ecirc;tre s&eacute;culaires en leurs couches profondes. <br>[They are busy already for three days nailing boards on the square. They erect a &ldquo;scaffold&rdquo; from which the master will speak to the people. Good countryfolk have come to lend a hand to the carpenters. Without any salary, but they know they will receive a tip, and they are so confident that God will repay their troubles in heaven, that they do not think at all they&apos;re being duped. About everywhere heaps of manure are removed, possibly in age-old deep layers (1). <small> Matthieu-Maxime Gorce, <a name="STVF" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#STVF"><cite title="source">Saint Vincent Ferrier</cite></a> (1924) 82</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
